  <title>GLib.Source.prototype.set_can_recurse</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function set_can_recurse(can_recurse: Boolean): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_source_set_can_recurse()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Sets whether a source can be called recursively. If <code>can_recurse</code> is
<code>true</code>, then while the source is being dispatched then this source
will be processed normally. Otherwise, all processing of this
source is blocked until the dispatch function returns.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>can_recurse</code></title>
  <p>whether recursion is allowed for this source</p>
</item>
